\b\i Overview and Important Info:\b0\i0\par
\pard\li360\par
Version 1.12 is a total update "mod" for Warzone 2100.  The goal of the v1.12 mod is to improve the sense of balance in Warzone play, with a focus on creating new opportunities and strategies to exploit, and to discourage the temptation of "ant-swarm" tactics.\par
\par
\b Version 1.12\b0  is a weapon-containing mod and therefore \b DOES NOT MIX\b0  with other weapon-containing mods, such as WZCK mods, mod-containing maps (e.g. "Citadel") or mod-containing AI's (like "Genghis Khan").\par
\par
\b Version 1.12 is designed to be run with stock v1.10 AI only.\b0   Various NEWST AI's, like the "Turtle" AI for example, are \b not\b0  compatible with Version 1.12 and will cause a Warzone crash if they are present when Version 1.12 is run.\par
\par
However, we the TWZ Group have plans to release a set of v1.12-compatible AI's, and will do so at a later date.\par
